com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.saf.handler
Interface IServiceDescriptor

All Superinterfaces:
ICommonDescriptor
public interface IServiceDescriptor
extends ICommonDescriptor

Describes an available service, including the EMF Model Element Type (getEType() as well as the fully qualified Java class getServiceType().

The EClass is available, but caution should be used in acquiring it as it can cause plugins to load.

This interface is not intended to be implemented by clients.

Method Summary
